Some of the greatest movie quotes of all time according to AFI

"Frankly, my dear, I dont give a damn" Gone With the Wind (1939)

"Im gonna make him an offer he cant refuse" The Godfather (1972)

"Toto I have a feeling were not in Kansas anymore" The Wizard of Oz (1942)

"Youre gonna need a bigger boat" Jaws (1975)

"Houston we have a problem" Apollo 13 (1995)
